


IMRGBTOHSI(3IM)        SDSC IMAGE LIBRARY         IMRGBTOHSI(3IM)



NAME
     ImRgbToHsi - Convert an RGB triplet to an HSI triplet

SYNOPSIS
     #include "im.h"

     void ImRgbToHsi( rgb, hsi )
          int  rgb[3];
          float     hsi[3];


DESCRIPTION
     ImRgbToHsi converts an RGB triplet in _r_g_b to an HSI  triplet
     returned in _h_s_i.

     Maximum and minimum values for the  different  color  values
     are:

           Channel     Minimum   Maximum    Type
8          ________________________________________
          red          0         255       Integer
          green        0         255       Integer
          blue         0         255       Integer
          hue          0.0       360.0     Integer
          saturation   0.0       1.0       Float
          intensity    0.0       1.0       Float

SEE ALSO
     ImIntro (3IM), ImErrNo (3IM), ImHsiToRgb (3IM)

